  <brief_title>Local Open-Label Access Study For Patients Who Completed A1481244 Study In Brazil</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Local, Multi-Centre, Extension, Open Label Access Study, To Provide Sildenafil Therapy For Patients Who Completed A1481244 Study And Are Judged By The Investigator To Derive Clinical Benefit From Continued Treatment With Sildenafil , Prior To Reimbursement And Availability For Patients In Brazil.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
